	<div class="intro-section">
		<p class="lead">A quality fence is a valuable investment in your Stockton property, but costs of $5,000 to $15,000 or more can strain any budget. The good news is that multiple financing options can help you get the fence you need now while spreading payments over time. Here's how to choose the right financing for your situation.</p>
